    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・基于物理的塔防</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人没有血量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握物理规律，将敌人推下关卡，抵御一波又一波的进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/32b12bc7e6675531318d053e0d718f10.poster.avif?t=1770859185\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/32b12bc7e6675531318d053e0d718f10.webm?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/32b12bc7e6675531318d053e0d718f10.mp4?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・构建完美卡组</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏都独一无二。发现改变游戏规则的新塔牌和升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/93ac73632424b5fc35b0c22332c5b5d2.poster.avif?t=1770859185\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/93ac73632424b5fc35b0c22332c5b5d2.webm?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/93ac73632424b5fc35b0c22332c5b5d2.mp4?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・发现创意联动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塔楼通过物理力量协同作战，而非脚本效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >缩小敌人使其更容易推动，或冒险放大敌人以获得<strong>更多奖励。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/1705cffc32f2e5068c02c2fc563fe74d.poster.avif?t=1770859185\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/1705cffc32f2e5068c02c2fc563fe74d.webm?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/1705cffc32f2e5068c02c2fc563fe74d.mp4?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・你能走多远？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无尽模式中测试你最强的防御，对抗越来越难的敌人波次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在排行榜上竞争，看看你的构建实力如何。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/7b016b73d8b11c6d1d7ac4140e5f2603.poster.avif?t=1770859185\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/7b016b73d8b11c6d1d7ac4140e5f2603.webm?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084810/extras/7b016b73d8b11c6d1d7ac4140e5f2603.mp4?t=1770859185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
